From 6fabed4052176a18da9519fc14a18897ed4f820d Mon Sep 17 00:00:00 2001
From: Aaradhana Sahu <quic_aarasahu@quicinc.com>
Date: Sun, 19 Jan 2025 14:06:54 +0530
Subject: [PATCH] wifi: ath: create common testmode_i.h file for ath drivers
Git-commit: 6fabed4052176a18da9519fc14a18897ed4f820d
Patch-mainline: v6.15-rc1
References: jsc#PED-14425

User space application requires that the testmode interface
is exactly same between ath drivers. Move testmode_i.h file
in ath directory to ensure that all ath driver uses same testmode
interface instead of duplicating testmode_i.h for each ath drivers.

Tested-on: IPQ8074 hw2.0 AHB WLAN.HK.2.7.0.1-01744-QCAHKSWPL_SILICONZ-1
Tested-on: QCN9274 hw2.0 PCI WLAN.WBE.1.3.1-00173-QCAHKSWPL_SILICONZ-1

Signed-off-by: Aaradhana Sahu <quic_aarasahu@quicinc.com>
Reviewed-by: Aditya Kumar Singh <quic_adisi@quicinc.com>
Link: https://patch.msgid.link/20250119083657.1937557-2-quic_aarasahu@quicinc.com
Signed-off-by: Jeff Johnson <jeff.johnson@oss.qualcomm.com>
Acked-by: Takashi Iwai <tiwai@suse.de>

---
 drivers/net/wireless/ath/ath11k/testmode.c   | 80 ++++++++++----------
 drivers/net/wireless/ath/ath11k/testmode_i.h | 66 ----------------
 drivers/net/wireless/ath/testmode_i.h        | 66 ++++++++++++++++
 3 files changed, 106 insertions(+), 106 deletions(-)
 delete mode 100644 drivers/net/wireless/ath/ath11k/testmode_i.h
 create mode 100644 drivers/net/wireless/ath/testmode_i.h

